headline: Skyworks Solutions (SWKS): A Fresh Look at Valuation After Sector Jitters Triggered by Texas Instruments Forecast
summary: Shares of Skyworks Solutions (SWKS) slipped 3% after a disappointing outlook from Texas Instruments. This development heightened concerns about a slowing recovery across the broader semiconductor industry and cast a shadow over sector performance. See our latest analysis for Skyworks Solutions.
